videos.description: Nuni Omot passes up to Terry Matson who puts down a powerful dunk in transition for Baylor.
videos.headline: Matson hammers down a two-handed jam

videos.description: Trae Young gets past his defender and floats one in for his first field goal.
videos.headline: Young uses floater to score first basket

videos.description: Manu Lecomte whips a long pass to Mark Vital who throws it down with a two-handed jam for Baylor.
videos.headline: Lecomte's great pass leads to Vital dunk

videos.description: Trae Young passes down court to Kameron McGusty who scores a transition bucket for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Young's nice feed sets up McGusty layup
